name: REP Fitness AB-5000 ZeroGap Adjustable Bench
description: The AB-5000 ZeroGap Adjustable Bench from REP Fitness features a patented ZeroGap seat adjustment, 7 back pad angles, and 3 seat pad angles, providing a stable and customizable platform for various exercises.

name: Ironmaster Super Bench PRO V2
description: The Super Bench PRO V2 by Ironmaster offers 11 adjustable angles, a low profile height of 17.2 inches in flat position, and compatibility with various attachments, making it ideal for home gyms with limited space.

name: Marcy MD-857 Olympic Weight Bench
description: The Marcy MD-857 Olympic Weight Bench combines a preacher curl pad, leg developer, and adjustable back pad, offering a comprehensive solution for full-body workouts.

name: Bowflex 5.1S Stowable Bench
description: The Bowflex 5.1S Stowable Bench offers 6 adjustable positions, a 600-pound load capacity, and a unique folding design for easy storage, making it perfect for home gyms.

name: Rogue Adjustable Bench 3.0
description: The Rogue Adjustable Bench 3.0 features a 3x3” 11-gauge steel frame, 10 back pad positions, and 3 seat positions, providing unmatched stability and versatility for intense workouts.

name: Technogym Element+ Adjustable Bench
description: The Element+ Adjustable Bench from Technogym offers a modern aesthetic with 6 backrest positions and 3 seat positions, suitable for a variety of strength training exercises.

name: Everfit 9-in-1 Weight Bench
description: The Everfit 9-in-1 Weight Bench combines a bench press, leg developer, preacher curl, and more, offering a comprehensive workout solution in a compact design.

name: Adjustable Folding Weight Bench
description: This adjustable folding weight bench offers multiple incline positions, a sturdy steel frame, and a foldable design for easy storage, making it ideal for home fitness enthusiasts.

name: VIBESPARK Adjustable Weight Bench
description: The VIBESPARK Adjustable Weight Bench features a 600lbs capacity, multiple backrest positions, and includes resistance bands, providing a full-body workout solution.
